gladTeX is a preprocessor that enables the use of LaTeX maths within HTML 
code. The maths, embedded in <eq>..</eq> tags, as if within $$..$$ in 
LaTeX, is fed through latex and replaced by images.

Features:
 - Image alignment (baseline of equations agree with baseline of text)
 - Gif and Png support
 - Transparent background
 - Antialiasing 

Requires: latex, libgif and libpng, all included in stock Slackware

